ygData.messageBody:
Not to forget, Yiyang will sponsor ya with all ya lvl 1 to 20 scrolls. If
you can make him 'happy', he may 'fill' you up with those enchanted
jewelries which he get from his "boyfriend" Kellendil , hehe.

Btw, our hairy chest Trifrost is not a preferred kind, he is the hairy
kind, like to touch here touch there. The only reason for him to follow
the path of shaman is to gain SoW at early lvl, so that his victim can
never escape from his hairy 'hands', haha.

The only eception is the aqua gu niang, Sereph, which can sing faster than
SoW. SHe is a BI, her speed song allow her to train anyone SHe like to
leave her/his hands on. Sometime SHe play SM with her parang and has
record of mis-chop at vital "part" of some players.

Watch out!

Ziltus (How straight you wanna be today?)

p/s: I think I can go to FP practice smithing tonight. I will make only
banded gorget since they are the cheapest banded to make - with 2-3pp cost
each I think. If anyone wanna buy cheap medium size banded gorget at cost,
give me a tell tonight around 11pm. Thx.
